				<img class="hvres-variant-img lazy" data-original="/pic/kt/tjZcggmKDAe5mFl5alViAg.gif" /></span></div><p class="hvres-source">Dị thể</p>		<div class="hvres-meaning"><a href="/whv/诈"><span class="hvres-variant han">&#35784;</span></a><a href="/whv/醡"><span class="hvres-variant han">&#37281;</span></a><a href="/whv/𧧻"><span class="hvres-variant han">&#162299;</span></a><p class="gray small" style="padding-left:10px"><a href="/fonts.php">Không hiện chữ?</a></p></div><p class="hvres-source">Một số bài thơ có sử dụng</p>		<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/B%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-H%C6%B0u/Ch%C3%ADnh-nh%E1%BA%A1c-ph%E1%BB%A7-th%E1%BA%ADp-thi%C3%AAn-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-u%E1%BA%A9n-th%C3%A1n/poem-BlaXbMAErhPGmQ7RjzZKHA">Chính nhạc phủ thập thiên - Tượng uẩn thán - 正樂府十篇－橡媼嘆</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/B%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-H%C6%B0u/author-YaU63-B8n1CAEl8OjKg7AQ">Bì Nhật Hưu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/H%E1%BB%89-v%C4%83n-quan-qu%C3%A2n-d%C4%A9-l%C3%A2m-t%E1%BA%B7c-c%E1%BA%A3nh-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem--7aSmm5Sn3I7FvPVGG4inQ">Hỉ văn quan quân dĩ lâm tặc cảnh, nhị thập vận - 喜聞官軍已臨賊境二十韻</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Ph%C3%B3ng-ng%C3%B4n-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-SkQu35S419ovOtPhhC9AjA">Phóng ngôn kỳ 1 - 放言其一</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%A5n/poem-xfUL0RFU1M6WV9XOi__Sxg">Thiên vấn - 天問</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C6%AF/poem-S3xXMkhBR0_221hv5Tm5tA">Thương Ư - 商於</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/></div>		</div>
